These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, november
There 2 different types of food: potato, radish
1. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Birthday         | november | february |
| Food     | potato | radish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different games are played: snooker, bridge
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, january
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Game          | snooker     | bridge |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Birthday     | may   | january    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, blend
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
House: futuristic, colonial
1. the colonial house is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the chaman-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Cigar    | blend     | chaman |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| House   | futuristic         | colonial    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, mechanic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, pop
1. the mechanic is on the right of the firefighter##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the fan of pop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Flower          | begonia   | orchid  |
| Job         | firefighter | mechanic     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | pop         |

