The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, orchid
2 different pets are kept: cat, horse
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, havana
1. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsorchid is on the far left or far right##3
3. the electrician is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
