The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games
2 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle
There 2 different types of food: peach, grapes
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
2. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
3. the project-manager is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Job           | accountant | project-manager |
| Hobby   | filmmaking    | board-games      |
| Pet           | mouse      | turtle          |
| Food         | grapes | peach       |

