.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, doctor
2 different games are played: scrabble, bridge
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, green
1. the doctor is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person who likes yellow is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| Game         | scrabble          | bridge     |
| Color   | yellow        | green     |

 